{
  "stem": "20142.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And somehow we're standing like, glued on to one another in this column.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I can't tell how many were there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "There were-- for the two last wagons of the-- of the transport.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I would say there were between-- or maybe three-- there were somewhere around 300 people, youngsters, fairly healthy-looking and in good shape, that the-- the Germans suddenly send in some people from the camp.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And we knew that they were from the-- from Treblinka, because they had the striped uniform and the numbers on 'em.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they were cleaning out whatever people left behind.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the minute they were done cleaning, taking everything out, the Germans marched us-- us right in into this same wagon.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was quite surprising to us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And one of the inmates from Treblinka said, in Jewish, you are saved.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You are saved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Don't worry.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You are saved.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we couldn't understand what he meant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Healthy, fairly healthy-looking.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they were getting additional rations for the people from the Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were getting always something, or stealing, or organizing.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They never said in a camp that somebody stole something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They said that they were organizing it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this the way things were-- actually functioned.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But [INAUDIBLE] when we-- we when they-- they packed us up in the last two wagons, then we-- they closed up the doors and they gave us water to drink.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was quite unusual.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Germans never would give anybody anything, especially in a transport to-- to any other place.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "For about two hours.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From far away, we saw the camp.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And from the platform, when you stay in Treblinka, even today, from the selection platform, you see thousands of gravestones overlooking the-- the main camp.",
      "word_count": 25
    }
  ],
